title: Frank Lloyd Wright Doormat—Martin Welcome
description:
Adapted from Frank Lloyd Wright's® (American, 1867-1959) Pier Cluster window design for the Darwin D. Martin House in Buffalo New York, c. 1904. Our doormat is a unique architectural tribute made of natural handwoven coir fiber and durable black rubber.

  • Dimensions: 30 x 18 in.
  • Materials: natural coir fiber, rubber

Additional Shipping $15 per Order.

This item cannot be shipped to a destination outside the United States.
